g;-hemolytic streptococci), as well as Gram-negative aerobes - <i>Escherichia coli</i>, <i>Haemophilus influenzae</i> (including &szlig;-lactamase-producing ampicillin-resistant strains), <i>Klebsiella sp</i>, and <i>Proteus mirabilis</i>.', 'DrugBank', 0, 0, 0);
